reviews.content: This office is horrible, never return calls, staff is too young and rude. They have no personable skills at all, probably cheap help.  Always want patients to come in for prescription refills, supposedly due to a new federal law. Not true at all several people I know have thec EXACT same prescriptions I have and are required to see their dr once every six months, not every three months, another price gouging office. Do not go here, it's a waste of time and money.
